{"type": "article", "id": 29981, "title": "Alexander Wang要和阿迪联名，以及，COS 秋冬男装不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-07-22T02:48:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1027, "name": "彩妆"}, {"id": 3126, "name": "牛仔"}, {"id": 4595, "name": "戒指"}, {"id": 5368, "name": "古巴"}, {"id": 25091, "name": "奥运"}, {"id": 29722, "name": "秋冬季"}, {"id": 30488, "name": "设计师联名系列"}, {"id": 30489, "name": "全球总裁"}, {"id": 248, "name": "COS"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 977, "name": "Tom Ford"}, {"id": 1582, "name": "爱马仕"}, {"id": 1722, "name": "Alexander Wang"}, {"id": 2009, "name": "Christian Louboutin"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 2855, "name": "Tommy Hilfiger"}, {"id": 3132, "name": "Emilio Pucci"}, {"id": 17504, "name": "A.P.C."}, {"id": 30490, "name": "Sportmax"}, {"id": 1722, "name": "Alexander Wang"}, {"id": 17991, "name": "Alber Elbaz"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 67, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160722103756AsnzfXwKxDHWU2IR.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/alexander-wang-adidas-collaborate-10494358/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Alexander Wang 或将和 Adidas 推出联名系列</b></a>｜WWD 报道，Alexander Wang （王大仁）将会是 Adidas 下一位合作的设计师，联名系列即将推出。Adidas 和 Alexander Wang 方面都未对此作出回应，据传公司计划在 Alexander Wang 纽约时装周的走秀结束后发布联名系列，即 9 月 10 日。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/hermes-sales-rise-6-2-in-q2-10493876/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>爱马仕二季度增速超预期</b></a>｜凭借在日本、法国和美国市场的强劲势头，法国奢侈品牌爱马仕（Hermès）二季度营收表现超预期，收益获得 6.2% 的增长至 12.5 亿美元，恒定汇率下增幅则达到 8.1%，超出 5.6% 的预期。上半年销售额增长了 7.2%，去年同期的增长率为 8.8%。其中在 Birkin 和 Kelly 包的带动下，皮具、马具部门二季度销售额上涨了 15.2%，成衣及配饰部门有 3.9% 的跌幅。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/prestige/tom-ford-guillaume-jesel-named-president-tom-ford-beauty-10494600/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Tom Ford Beauty 高级副总裁将升任全球总裁</b></a>｜Tom Ford  美妆的高级副总裁、全球总经理 Guillaume Jesel 近日升任品牌全球总裁，7 月 1 日生效。在职两年期间，Guillaume Jesel 帮助品牌全球范围内实现两位数的增长，预估在截至 6 月 30 日的财年内，销售额超过 5 亿美元，比 2015 财年上涨了 29%。此前 Guillaume Jesel 在雅诗兰黛任管理职位有 14 年。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/christian-louboutin-outfits-cubas-olympics-team-10494610/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Christian Louboutin 为古巴队设计队服</b></a>｜以“红底鞋”闻名的 Christian Louboutin  最近为古巴国家队设计了参与里约奥运会的开幕式、闭幕式队服。Christian Louboutin 与前古巴专业手球队员 Henri Tai  合作，后者是一家专注运动服、生活方式服装的初创男装电商 SportyHenri.com 创始人。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>White Mountaineering 与“三叶草”继续合作，推出<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/adidas-white-mountaineering-2016-fall-winter-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">秋冬季的联名系列</a>：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722092353rnshTlN34bcQOLdq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607220923548xSIjCyu0Z4VQg2R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722092356vwaCiTpzyQmIXW3N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722092406V4bLuehZHSFJzoQl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607220924079lrUmiFntSfBJVj3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722092415qoUn9VwPy23kXTl1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754980\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>极简的 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/coss-2016-fall-winter-campaign-showcases-the-brands-knack-for-timeless-staples\" rel=\"nofollow\">COS 发布 2016 秋冬男装</a>：</p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607220925169KqduUBekopNhj5Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.755976\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722092517bDyUBNW4V7esRThw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.755976\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722092518Rzxka8wtBApTSnPF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.755976\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722092528H0Av1gmJDB3dwGhU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.755976\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/advertising/hilfiger-denims-digital-campaign-features-hailey-baldwin-and-lucky-blue-smith-10493573/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tommy Hilfiger 发布秋季牛仔系列广告</a>，Hailey Baldwin 与 Lucky Blue Smith 出镜拍摄：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722102450e4K9azX28bE3Wxmj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.981108\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722102451zdtb4Ta5rfnGMcWB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607221024532KqOc9MFt8TDmjRA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.744641\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607220922107LgkMQ2Yvlw3GmrR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722092210m2oULQ9q3vRgXVy5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722092216Ri1qyXMDGTY2u8HQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p>Dior 推出了一个<a href=\"http://www.buro247.me/jewellery-and-watches/news/just-in-dior-presents-the-lucky-dior-rings.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">戒指系列 Lucky</a>， 7 枚戒指上分别镶嵌蜜蜂、铃兰、五角星、首字母缩写、四叶草等形状，代表品牌创始人 Christian Dior 童年的一些重要时刻：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722101250HTg6Up7bR0cwdrqV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722101251wW0iQ4dYLhSnG3xX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722101251hnMDO1U0idHe7IXw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722101251eiQMhmrF4VR6dfnG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722101252pSGl6BHJk9FZ2XmV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722101251IiALGv59zN8tjYfa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722101251yj8fOZcSzgsMtm59.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>COMME des GARÇONS 发布<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/07/20/dsm-new-comme-des-garcons/\" rel=\"nofollow\">全新 Play tee 设计</a>：</p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722103057Hw561EAqX3KzkLiy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722103057oeQGVmxpOTCA8fsl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722103057gxzLFMhy6qQfDEAB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img sr